ardinality of a field from 1 to n or n to 1</td>
<td class=3D"tf-rowspan-1 tf-colspan-1 confluenceTd" colspan=3D"1">No</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"tf-rowspan-1 tf-colspan-1 confluenceTd" colspan=3D"1">Add new =
http status code</td>
